data.description: Pool, pool, pool! Do not miss out on the opportunity to own a home in one of the best neighborhoods in Highlands Ranch. Multiple homes of the same model and on the same street have sold in the 900s!!! This ranch-style home is nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac and has no back neighbor. With a whopping 4,437 total square feet, you will own one of the biggest homes in the neighborhood. It features a heated private pool that was designed for entertaining family and friends. This pool has the capability of running year-round if you desire. Imagine enjoying beautiful mountain views and sunsets from your backyard while you sip champagne. Stay warm and cozy this winter around the gas fireplace in the living room. Newer laminate flooring and new paint throughout the main floor gives this home a nice modern look. The oversized master bedroom includes a walk-in closet and an attached 5-piece master bath. The sunroom is a great addition for plant lovers. There is room to grow and add additional rooms and bedrooms with the 1,000 unfinished square feet. This home is literally right next to good schools, parks, Links Golf Course, and great restaurants.
